      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready to hit the pavement with its next owner. Come take it for a spin, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
