    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 996.2 Carrera 2, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus. This example is a true driver\u2019s specification, boasting a 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit, rear main seal replacement, and a recent water pump and low-temp thermostat install. The suspension geometry remains tight, delivering the communicative feedback and rear-engine weight bias enthusiasts crave. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the engine pulls linearly to redline with zero bore scoring symptoms. A turn-key performance machine ready for the track or the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
