    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality, having been meticulously maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you may find the occasional minor stone chip or light swirl mark consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all electronic features\u2014from the premium navigation system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has followed a strict service schedule, resulting in a smooth engine note and crisp, reliable gear shifts. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brake feel is firm and responsive. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy a premium driving experience. Detailed service records are available for your peace of mind.",
      "price": 36500.0,
